name: Nubs and Friends 2014 Calendar
description:
Let Nubs and his Friends keep you organized all year long! Our  6" x 6" full-color calendar (12" x 6" when open) will appeal to your imagination and warm your heart. 

This calendar is a very limited edition run, and is already more than 50% sold out. Order soon to avoid disappointment!

Donation: $16 per calendar

Please note that, pursuant to our status as a 501(c)4 organization, this item is considered a gift in return for a donation.

name:
Nubs: A Little Bird with a Big Story
(1-4 books)
description:
In October 2012, Nubs (the budgie the organization is named for) and over 340 other parakeets were rescued from the home of a bird hoarder. The Washington Park Zoo (Michigan City, Indiana), generously adopted almost all of Nubs’ flock in December 2012. The Zoo, which features many rescued animals, provided an indoor/outdoor aviary exhibit for the flock to live. 

In September 2013, friends of NUBS upgraded the indoor aviary to provide the flock with a bright, healthy environment for their indoor winter home!

Donation: 1-4 books @ $12.95/book

Please note that, pursuant to our status as a 501(c)4 organization, this item is considered a gift in return for a donation.
